Rating: 1
I wish that I had read these reviews before making this cake for my daughter's birthday! When I made the cake, I suspected that there was far too little water, but I didn't adjust. The cake was VERY dry and disappointing. The frosting was too sweet, but it might have been OK if the cake hadn't been so dry.

