Rating: 4
I made this cake for Father's Day and everyone loved it. It was easy to make and came out rich and moist. (I increased the water to 1 1/3 cup)

Rating: 2
This cake was a dissappointment. The cake was very dry. I'm wondering if there was a typo in the recipe. It called for 1/3 cup water. The recipe on the box of cake mix called for 1 and 1/3 cups water. The batter was very sticky and hard to work with. The cake ended up like a big brownie. I thought it would be good, but it was not moist and chewy. The frosting and filling was great, but the cake needs to be moister.